---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" noIndex={true}>
  <section class="legal-page section">
    <div class="container container--sm">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-page__updated">Last updated: July 2026</p>

      <div class="legal-page__content">
        <h2>1. Information I Collect</h2>
        <p>When you use this website, I may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> Your name, email address, company name, and message content when you submit the contact form.</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Anonymous usage data including pages visited, time spent, browser type, and device information through Google Analytics.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Essential cookies for site functionality and analytics cookies for understanding usage patterns.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How I Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to your inquiries and project requests</li>
          <li>To improve the website experience</li>
          <li>To understand how visitors use the website</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>I do not sell, trade, or transfer your personal information to third parties. Your contact form data is processed through Web3Forms, which acts as a data processor on my behalf.</p>

        <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Contact form submissions are retained for the duration of our business relationship. Analytics data is retained according to Google Analytics' default retention policies.</p>

        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Opt out of analytics tracking</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any privacy-related questions, contact me at <a href="mailto:hello@arunalexgeorge.online">hello@arunalexgeorge.online</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding-top: calc(72px + var(--space-16)); }

  .legal-page h1 { margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }

  .legal-page__updated {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .legal-page__content h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .legal-page__content p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .legal-page__content ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .legal-page__content li {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .legal-page__content a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
